videos.headline: Wildcats RB Rodriguez Jr. says the sky is the limit
videos.description: Kentucky's Chris Rodriguez Jr. believes his career-high of 206 rushing yards stemmed from preparation at practice and support from his teammates.

videos.headline: Rodriguez Jr., Kentucky fend off Mizzou in SEC thriller
videos.description: In a game to remember, Wildcats RB Chris Rodriguez Jr. explodes for 206 rushing yards and four total touchdowns to top Missouri, 35-28.
